This repository is for a project to build a standalone device to play a Pandora internet radio stream, based on a cheap wireless router, OpenWRT, pianobar, and Arduino.

For more information:

http://www.blackbrass.org/wiki/index.php?title=Standalone_Pandora_Player

Blog posts:
http://www.blackbrass.org/blog/2011/01/building-a-standalone-pandora-player/
http://www.blackbrass.org/blog/2011/01/testing-openwrt-on-a-slug/

